022package org.biojava.nbio.structure.io;
023
024/**
025 * An exception during the parsing of a PDB file.
026 *
027 * @author Andreas Prlic, Thomas Down, Benjamin Schuster-B&ouml;ckler
028 */
029
030public class PDBParseException extends Exception{
031        public static final long serialVersionUID = 219047230178423923l;
032        /**
033         * Constructs a PDBParseException object.
034         *
035         * @param s  a String ...
036         */
037
038        public PDBParseException(String s) {
039                super(s);
040        }
041        /**
042         * Constructs a PDBParseException object.
043         *
044         * @param t  a Throwable object
045         * @param s  a String ...
046         */
047        public PDBParseException ( String s,Throwable t) {
048                super(s, t);
049        }
050        /**
051         * Constructs a PDBParseException object.
052         *
053         * @param t  a Throwable object
054         */
055        public PDBParseException (Throwable t) {
056                super(t);
057        }
058}
